# 🏗️ Project Overview

This is a Next.js project with TypeScript and Tailwind CSS. The project follows the Next.js App Router architecture.

## 🛠️ Main Technologies
- [Next.js](mdc:https:/nextjs.org) - React framework
- TypeScript - Type-safe JavaScript
- [Tailwind CSS](mdc:https:/tailwindcss.com) - Utility-first CSS framework
- React - UI library

## 📁 Project Structure
- `src/app` - Contains all pages and API routes using Next.js App Router
- `src/components` - Reusable React components
- `src/utils` - Utility functions and helpers
- `src/lib` - Core libraries and configurations
- `src/types` - TypeScript type definitions
- `src/assets` - Static assets like images

## 📄 Key Files
- [package.json](mdc:package.json) - Project dependencies and scripts
- [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json) - TypeScript configuration
- [tailwind.config.ts](mdc:tailwind.config.ts) - Tailwind CSS configuration
- [next.config.ts](mdc:next.config.ts) - Next.js configuration
- [src/app/layout.tsx](mdc:src/app/layout.tsx) - Root layout component
